{"tid":1854481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【樓市堪憂】香港負資產宗數按季激增1.4倍","createTime":"2020-01-31T13:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:46:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"024ea6c11a7dfa9f9d49bc728d9fbc895f031167","tid":1854481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"香港金融管理局公布，負資產住宅按揭貸款的最新調查結果，負資產宗數由2019年第3季末的53宗，增加至第4季末的128宗，按季增加141%。這些個案大部分為銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款，少數涉及按揭保險計劃的貸款。這些貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n必須注意的是，此調查所得數字僅涉及銀行提供並已知道為負資產的一按貸款(即欠受訪機構的未償還貸款額超過按揭物業的當前市值)，當中並不包括涉及二按，而連同二按計算屬於負資產貸款的住宅按揭貸款。由於銀行沒有客戶在二按下的未償還貸款的資料，因此無法知悉其中有多少宗屬於負資產貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200131/bkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200131%2Fbkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=65560b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200131/bkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5970d4fa39dabbe239563c7495aebdfe1ca0c678","tid":1854481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a71fdaaf91fb8fd0bdb50a664e2d570381c9417","tid":1854481,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬又要訓街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acab85ce7edcd30a0ebdd12c9d615f53c99fcc18","tid":1854481,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"好少啫個基數咁細"},{"pid":"8388bd19bd92ea1eeb512a8de9a3d2c9e24bc9a3","tid":1854481,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"藍絲朋友（死不足惜果種）<br />\n<br />\n3個月前，果時仲聽佢話9成按揭想買樓<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">o</span><br />\n話做樓奴等一國一制用，買樓準備收成期，<br />\n我哋就等香港有美團，淘寶免運費，唔洗過關，<br />\n年年食玩爽！<br />\n<br />\n成日係群組串鳩我深黃，睇野好灰，<br />\n抗爭可以當飯食咩？人生緊係買樓結婚生仔等收成<br />\n<br />\n仲成日用admin功能打壓我<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">o</span><br />\n<br />\n（今次你哋仲唔仆街.jpg)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f17b8a25840416d869976a5a3e0208dca56d63a","tid":1854481,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYbth4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYbth4F.png&h=659c0f8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"486dda111efd101b2a0040f5a1f3da4ccf151e01","tid":1854481,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"負資產小事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加埋失業率升先好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fc22593a030ae46c2d6240c23e63b7f94406cc","tid":1854481,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"024ea6c11a7dfa9f9d49bc728d9fbc895f031167","tid":1854481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"香港金融管理局公布，負資產住宅按揭貸款的最新調查結果，負資產宗數由2019年第3季末的53宗，增加至第4季末的128宗，按季增加141%。這些個案大部分為銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款，少數涉及按揭保險計劃的貸款。這些貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n必須注意的是，此調查所得數字僅涉及銀行提供並已知道為負資產的一按貸款(即欠受訪機構的未償還貸款額超過按揭物業的當前市值)，當中並不包括涉及二按，而連同二按計算屬於負資產貸款的住宅按揭貸款。由於銀行沒有客戶在二按下的未償還貸款的資料，因此無法知悉其中有多少宗屬於負資產貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200131/bkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200131%2Fbkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=65560b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200131/bkn-20200131184807152-0131_00842_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"百幾宗遮...........<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o24FTN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo24FTN9.png&h=80b0b75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12oWr8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12oWr8a.png&h=0988edf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd22da33adb6e252efe39b42c2abcf7b0203dfc7","tid":1854481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}